    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Rusty Dudes》是一款管理雇佣兵团队的游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/d0d5090874aa52e4409a3b08606fb295.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/d0d5090874aa52e4409a3b08606fb295.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/d0d5090874aa52e4409a3b08606fb295.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择不同的关卡任务、雇佣兵和独特的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/74508ff0a9979e15ea6a3bc31483f3ff.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/74508ff0a9979e15ea6a3bc31483f3ff.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/74508ff0a9979e15ea6a3bc31483f3ff.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在竞技场地图上检验你团队的实力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/c49f42e462cae2f3a022ff6a2765f77e.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/c49f42e462cae2f3a022ff6a2765f77e.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/c49f42e462cae2f3a022ff6a2765f77e.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用机动性和主动技能生存下来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/3b3543d226dd61271e6e3ffcfcbd6a7b.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/3b3543d226dd61271e6e3ffcfcbd6a7b.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/3b3543d226dd61271e6e3ffcfcbd6a7b.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成额外任务还是带着现有的资源撤退？你是Rusty Dudes的领导者，选择权在你手中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/afeb5e3f9f2913399e6b890473f7f0f3.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/afeb5e3f9f2913399e6b890473f7f0f3.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/afeb5e3f9f2913399e6b890473f7f0f3.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还在等什么？快出发吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/90139ae6f7c59f25c65561a39928aa07.poster.avif?t=1737597448\" width=600 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/90139ae6f7c59f25c65561a39928aa07.webm?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164830/extras/90139ae6f7c59f25c65561a39928aa07.mp4?t=1737597448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
